data.description: Welcome to Greene Tree Gated Community. Here is a rare opportunity to own this lovely freshly painted  well maintained townhouse Large price reduction!! Contract fell through, property being sold As Is. Seller will make no repairs!!! This large  contemporary Townhouse has 3 bedrooms with 3.5 baths. It has many updated features. Beautiful living room with fireplace, separate dinning room and eat in kitchen. Stainless steel appliances, lots of kitchen cabinets with  granite countertops.  New carpet, gleaming hardwood floors. Large Master bedroom with huge walk in closet. Finished basement with full bathroom.
